      <txt c="X" a="X" r="X" s="2" w="850" x="40" y="80" delay="0" pt="1" e="-3" align="left">If you promise to pay for the foreign government official’s dinner in an expensive restaurant, in order to gain business advantages to which you would not otherwise be entitled.

